# Post a Match Screen\
\
## Purpose\
Allow users to create a match request\
\
## Sections\
1. Sports selections\
2. Event name\
3. Start /end date and time \
4. Players needed\
5.match type: join or request to join\
6. Skill level:beginner,intermediate,advanced\
7.price/per player\
8. Description field\
9. CTA: Post Match\
\
## Constraints\
- Must be completed in \uc0\u8804  3 steps\
- Mobile-first design}